<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />早上好，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗨！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />晚上好，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_04" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哟，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我把堆成山的纸箱整理完，<delay20 />
终于有时间休息一下了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的非常感谢你，<delay20 />
在我搬来第一天<delay8 />就来看我。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谢谢你！</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把家里大致整理完以后，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就出来一边跟邻居打招呼，<delay8 />
一边在<tag a="110" b="32" />上到处转转。<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上<delay8 />都是些很有意思的家伙呢！<delay frames="40" />
我好期待今后的生活啊！</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我正在<tag a="110" b="32" />上<delay8 />到处走走看看。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有了一些和昨天不一样的发现，<delay20 />
感觉很有意思呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 />真是越了解，
就越喜欢这座<tag a="110" b="32" />呢～</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在这<tag a="110" b="33" />的生活，<delay20 />
我已经渐渐开始习惯了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聊过以后发现，大家都很亲切热情呢！<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这真的是一座很棒的<tag a="110" b="32" />！</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />对了！<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我今天来就是想给你这个，<delay20 />
所以我才一直把它带在身上的！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />差点就要忘了呢。</message>
	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我还没有把这个给你，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />差点就忘了呢！</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay20 />
在我的老家<delay8 />是件很常用的东西呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这算是伴手礼，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />请不用客气，收下吧！</message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这是<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay20 />
在我的老家人气非常高呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过在这座<tag a="110" b="32" /><delay8 />好像很稀有吧？<delay frames="40" />
我接下来也很可能会有需要麻烦你的时候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总之，这你就收下吧！</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="007_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得我们可以成为很好的朋友！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今后请多指教啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，<delay20 />
今后作为同一座<tag a="110" b="32" />的伙伴，
请多多关照！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今后可能有不少需要麻烦你的时候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />请多多关照啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
